    "name": "Vigorus",
    "steam_appid": 1840150,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840150/extras/41558710a8322a5de88dec54256022c0.avif?t=1714092217\" width=614 height=248 /></span><br>《薇尔与小迪》是一款以节奏玩法为主的2D横版平台闯关游戏。<br>在蜃怪肆虐的奇异世界中找到自己的节奏，以伞为剑盾，邂逅青蛙小迪，与千奇百怪的幻想生物翩翩起舞。是噩梦？是现实？失去记忆的薇尔究竟在为何而战，又是谁在阻止她在仿佛黑童话般的世界中找到出口？通过重重困难，等待着她的又是怎样的结局？<br>在律动中找寻时机闪避致命的威胁，发动自己的能力突破难关，收集关于薇尔散落的零落记忆，在只言片语中寻找关于整个世界的秘密。<br>让我们随着音符击碎这噩梦！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >内容特色</h2><br><strong>跟随节拍</strong><br>在音乐节拍上退治敌人，注意聆听音乐，识别并预判敌人的攻击模式并在正确的时机上打出漂亮的连击。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840150/extras/e5bb4c78861fa03e39a746dbce8feb22.poster.avif?t=1714092217\" width=500 height=142 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840150/extras/e5bb4c78861fa03e39a746dbce8feb22.webm?t=1714092217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840150/extras/e5bb4c78861fa03e39a746dbce8feb22.mp4?t=1714092217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>活用技能</strong><br>使用不同的技能让对敌操作更加行云流水，注重攻击、防御、闪避还是预判，这些都取决于你自己。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840150/extras/c15748c58d101a0764c496fde8bd6bf2.poster.avif?t=1714092217\" width=500 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840150/extras/c15748c58d101a0764c496fde8bd6bf2.webm?t=1714092217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840150/extras/c15748c58d101a0764c496fde8bd6bf2.mp4?t=1714092217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840150/extras/f704558111d16d2ef8679a6940adc0cf.poster.avif?t=1714092217\" width=500 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840150/extras/f704558111d16d2ef8679a6940adc0cf.webm?t=1714092217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840150/extras/f704558111d16d2ef8679a6940adc0cf.mp4?t=1714092217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>碎片故事</strong><br>在一无所知的世界中寻找自我，于每一个可以探索的事物中寻找记忆的碎片，并让事实真相浮出水面。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840150/extras/e3074f8d5d82f7c1f400a8a8ea375fa7.poster.avif?t=1714092217\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840150/extras/e3074f8d5d82f7c1f400a8a8ea375fa7.webm?t=1714092217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840150/extras/e3074f8d5d82f7c1f400a8a8ea375fa7.mp4?t=1714092217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于我们</h2><br>各位好！我们是独立游戏开发团队hagicians。《薇尔与小迪》这款游戏是由我们团队6人历时一年半研发的作品。这款游戏期初源于我们学生阶段的毕业设计作品，在毕业后我们各奔东西，团队成员分散在不同的时区，但仍是抽出时间将这款游戏进行打磨，并最终带到了这个平台。<br><br>《薇尔与小迪》是一款节奏平台类游戏，玩家将在奇妙的世界中开启一段音乐冒险。节奏化身为武器，节奏化身为特殊能力，节奏构成这个世界的全部，在音乐的带领下翩翩起舞，走向神秘的世界深渊。本游戏期初游戏的灵感是来源于儿童绘本，毕竟我们的插画师画的太好了！并且团队成员都很喜欢《魔法少女小圆》这部作品，也成为了这款游戏的灵感（是不是这里有剧透？）动感的音乐配上童真的画面（笑）别有一番氛围。<br><br>本游戏目前正在公开测试阶段，仍有瑕疵，还请大家谅解。如果在游戏中遇到问题或有想法和建议，欢迎联系我们，您的每一条反馈都对我们无比重要，我们的邮箱地址是： <a href=\"mailto:hagicians.official@gmail.com\">hagicians.official@gmail.com</a> <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840150/extras/fe85ebe55624e836fcb0675b7cdad5ac.avif?t=1714092217\" width=615 height=665 /></span><br><br>喜欢Vigorus的音乐吗？欢迎戳以下链接享用原声合集：<br><br><br><br>想要了解更多关于《薇尔与小迪》资讯&amp;打赏开发团队一杯奶茶，欢迎关注：<br><br>官方微博：@薇尔与小迪Vigorus<br>官方推特：@hagicians<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840150/extras/958af1b15aada940abfc5a9fa63a4391.avif?t=1714092217\" width=614 height=176 /></span><br><br>欢迎提出您的想法与建议，您的每一条反馈都对我们无比重要！",
